summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2016 DUTCHMAN ASPEN TRAIL. WHILE BEING OPERATED ON THE HIGHWAY, THE BUMPER DETACHED FROM THE TRAILER WITHOUT WARNING. THE VEHICLE WAS TAKEN TO THE INDEPENDENT MECHANIC WHERE IT WAS DIAGNOSED THAT THE WELDS WERE DEFECTIVE AND NEEDED TO BE REPLACED. THE VEHICLE WAS TAKEN TO THE CONTACT'S RESIDENCE. THE DEALER WAS NOT CONTACTED. THE MANUFACTURER WAS CONTACTED, BUT OFFERED NO ASSISTANCE. THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS NOT APPLICABLE.   UPDATED 11/06/17*LJ  *JS
